- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on analyzing discussions in an online health community. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the development of supervised classifiers for topic classification. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper deals with a health-related topic and the impact of online communities on patients. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with the classification of text data.
